Jesse Vint https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jesse_Vint 0 Jesse Lee Vint III is an American actor, film director and screenwriter. He acted in the films Macon County Line (1974), Black Oak Conspiracy (1977) and Forbidden World (1982). Jesse_Lee_Vint_III is an_American_actor , film_director_and_screenwriter .
